a non-vegan. Now in my very first nugget ever,
I touched on the environmental impact of the

00:00:10.450 --> 00:00:14.299
animal products industry. Today we're going
to compare the benefits the environment that

00:00:14.299 --> 00:00:19.290
the typical going green methods have, to the
impact that you have by making shifts in your

00:00:19.290 --> 00:00:24.600
diet. Often times the most passionate, vigilant,
