00:02:54.040 --> 00:02:59.689
be saving at most 8.51 trees. Whereas if you
avoid just 1 pound of beef, you're saving

00:02:59.689 --> 00:03:04.340
45 to 55 trees. Now if you went an entire
year without eating any beef, you'd be saving

00:03:04.340 --> 00:03:10.730
3,432 trees. By not eating beef for an entire
year, and we're not even talking about any

00:03:10.730 --> 00:03:17.020
other animal products at this point, you would
still be saving 3,406.49 more trees than if

00:03:17.020 --> 00:03:21.630
you didn't use any paper for the entire year
