00:04:10.719 --> 00:04:16.200
just beef, saves 5.5 tons of CO2. And now
for a simplified version - you could drive

00:04:16.200 --> 00:04:21.380
about 600 miles from the CO2 that's produced
by 1 pound of beef. Now believe it or not,

00:04:21.380 --> 00:04:25.060
